梨花壓海棠》，就係咁解。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T10:23:51.000Z","msg":"又學到野"},{"pid":"07ddce47d65b13b55dbf9065a2d789219d81b8c3","tid":2200461,"uid":741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"acf2fa4b114c9c62dfb73af49be2d3a4428e574d","tid":2200461,"uid":145096,"like":199,"dislike":2,"score":197,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T02:09:14.000Z","msg":"林靖恩出生於<span class=\"red\">中國台灣</span>，她的家境本身還是相當不錯的算是一個中產階級，她的母親是一名教授父親從事音樂工作，家庭收入相當可觀<br />\n<br />\n一睇到依度就唔洗睇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T10:36:08.000Z","msg":"Same here"},{"pid":"756e7c1fbe097b8ab52346f311bff6b52128bb35","tid":2200461,"uid":35508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T10:36:45.000Z","msg":"拉垃圾post<br />\n好噁心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f8231f3b7dd7a1a9e30475c6b870d9851fe6898","tid":2200461,"uid":222448,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T10:58:49.000Z","msg":"見到中蟈台灣四隻字已經唔想睇落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"527939d9c07a9a42216b72b20c5ed78a7c7bbde1","tid":2200461,"uid":22902,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T12:09:26.000Z","msg":"呢句&quot;曾因「忘年戀」爆紅的17歲少女林靖恩，時隔七年，女孩已失去純真&quot;要出現幾多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"979d77683c5eb15f0a0749de4f6d48c3221bdae3","tid":2200461,"uid":367093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T13:12:25.000Z","msg":"點嘴得落⋯"},{"pid":"c7919e6c8351ee4c269712820550e5df51e2afb2","tid":2200461,"uid":102010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7714b1afb2f8f965952090f5853c840554e1d133","tid":2200461,"uid":25345,"like":6,"dislike":32,"score":-26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T04:10:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://fbhost1.imgscloud.com/b/ei/CH04682.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffbhost1.imgscloud.com%2Fb%2Fei%2FCH04682.jpg&d=O8bnHDCsQiwN1SoPxP513cIAfqyfHgkV2drMeooGLQQ%3D&h=7ff27